node_5.subject: carmen ortiz
node_5.description: This is carmen ortiz's plan for Friday March 07: Wake up and complete the morning routine at 7:00 am., Arrive at Supermarket and start work at 9:00 am., Assist customers and manage store operations until lunch break at 12:00 pm., Have lunch at 12:00 pm., Return to work and continue helping customers at 1:00 pm., Take a short break and browse economic news at 3:00 pm., Leave work to attend a family gathering at the Gardner family's house at 4:00 pm., Deliver a speech on the future development of the virtual economy at 4:05 pm., Have a fierce argument with Carlos in the guest bedroom at 4:10 pm., Conclude the family gathering and head to the Moonlight Tavern Bar at 5:00 pm., Encounter Carlos again and continue the argument at 5:30 pm., Eat dinner at the Moonlight Tavern Bar at 8:00 pm., Leave the Moonlight Tavern Bar at 8:30 pm., Reflect on the day's events at home and prepare for bed at 10:00 pm., Go to bed at 11:00 pm..
